Name: :code:`month`
Description: Month of year ranging from 1 (January) through 12 (December).

Name: :code:`day_type`
Description: Day of week ranging from 1 (Monday) through 7 (Sunday).

Name: :code:`hour`
Description: Hour of day ranging from 1 to 24.

Name: :code:`daylight_savings_status`
Description: Boolean that indicates if the current day is daylight savings period.

Name: :code:`outdoor_dry_bulb_temperature`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature.

Name: :code:`outdoor_dry_bulb_temperature_predicted_6h`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature predicted 6 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`outdoor_dry_bulb_temperature_predicted_12h`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature predicted 12 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`outdoor_dry_bulb_temperature_predicted_24h`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature predicted 24 hours ahead

Name: :code:`outdoor_relative_humidity`
Description: Outdoor relative humidity.

Name: :code:`outdoor_relative_humidity_predicted_6h`
Description: Outdoor relative humidity predicted 6 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`outdoor_relative_humidity_predicted_12h`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature predicted 12 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`outdoor_relative_humidity_predicted_24h`
Description: Outdoor dry bulb temperature predicted 24 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`diffuse_solar_irradiance`
Description: Diffuse solar irradiance.

Name: :code:`diffuse_solar_irradiance_predicted_6h`
Description: Diffuse solar irradiance predicted 6 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`diffuse_solar_irradiance_predicted_12h`
Description: Diffuse solar irradiance predicted 12 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`diffuse_solar_irradiance_predicted_24h`
Description: Diffuse solar irradiance predicted 24 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`direct_solar_irradiance`
Description: Direct solar irradiance.

Name: :code:`direct_solar_irradiance_predicted_6h`
Description: Direct solar irradiance predicted 6 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`direct_solar_irradiance_predicted_12h`
Description: Direct solar irradiance predicted 12 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`direct_solar_irradiance_predicted_24h`
Description: Direct solar irradiance predicted 24 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`carbon_intensity`
Description: Grid carbon emission rate.

Name: :code:`indoor_dry_bulb_temperature`
Description: Zone volume-weighted average building dry bulb temperature.

Name: :code:`average_unmet_cooling_setpoint_difference`
Description: Zone volume-weighted average difference between `indoor_dry_bulb_temperature` and cooling temperature setpoints.

Name: :code:`indoor_relative_humidity`
Description: Zone volume-weighted average building relative humidity.

Name: :code:`non_shiftable_load`
Description: Total building non-shiftable plug and equipment loads.

Name: :code:`solar_generation`
Description: PV electricity generation.

Name: :code:`cooling_storage_soc`
Description: State of the charge (SOC) of the `cooling_storage` from 0 (no energy stored) to 1 (at full capacity).

Name: :code:`heating_storage_soc`
Description: State of the charge (SOC) of the `heating_storage` from 0 (no energy stored) to 1 (at full capacity).

Name: :code:`dhw_storage_soc`
Description: State of the charge (SOC) of the `dhw_storage` (domestic hot water storage) from 0 (no energy stored) to 1 (at full capacity).

Name: :code:`electrical_storage_soc`
Description: State of the charge (SOC) of the `electrical_storage` from 0 (no energy stored) to 1 (at full capacity).

Name: :code:`net_electricity_consumption`
Description: Total building electricity consumption.

Name: :code:`electricity_pricing`
Description: Electricity rate.

Name: :code:`electricity_pricing_predicted_6h`
Description: Electricity rate predicted 6 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`electricity_pricing_predicted_12h`
Description: Electricity rate predicted 12 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`electricity_pricing_predicted_24h`
Description: Electricity rate predicted 24 hours ahead.

Name: :code:`cooling_device_cop`
Description: :code:`cooling_device` Carnot cycle COP based solely on temperature difference between heat source and sink.

Name: :code:`heating_device_cop`
Description: :code:`heating_device` Carnot cycle COP based solely on temperature difference between heat source and sink.

Name: :code:`cooling_demand`
Description: Cooling energy supplied by :code:`cooling_device` and :code:`cooling_storage` for space cooling.

Name: :code:`heating_demand`
Description: Heating energy supplied by :code:`heating_device` and :code:`heating_storage` for space heating.

Name: :code:`dhw_demand`
Description: Heating energy supplied by :code:`dhw_device` and :code:`dhw_storage` for DHW heating.

Name: :code:`cooling_electricity_consumption`
Description: :code:`cooling_device` net electricity consumption in meeting :code:`cooling_demand` and :code:`cooling_storage` demand.

Name: :code:`heating_electricity_consumption`
Description: :code:`heating_device` net electricity consumption in meeting :code:`heating_demand` and :code:`heating_storage` demand.

Name: :code:`dhw_electricity_consumption`
Description: :code:`dhw_device` net electricity consumption in meeting :code:`dhw_demand` and :code:`dhw_storage` demand.

Name: :code:`indoor_dry_bulb_temperature_set_point`
Description: Zone volume-weighted average building dry bulb temperature set point.

Name: :code:`indoor_dry_bulb_temperature_delta`
Description: Absolute difference between :code:`indoor_dry_bulb_temperature` and :code:`indoor_dry_bulb_temperature_set_point` observations.

Name: :code:`power_outage`
Description: Integer signal indicating power outage at time step (1) or not (0).
